    "summary": "UptimeRobot exposes two HTTP APIs on `api.uptimerobot.com` (the authenticated v3 REST API and a public Quick Monitor Setup API for agent-created monitors) plus a hosted MCP server at `https://mcp.uptimerobot.com/mcp` authenticated by OAuth or API key.",
